HTTP-      ENGLISH                SQL
------    ---------              ----------

GET     Get a list of songs      --SELECT
POST     Create a new songs     -- INSERT
DELETE    Remove a songs       -- DELETE
PUT      Modify an existing songs  --UPDATE

CRUD --aka

Create
Read
Update 
Delete

GET /monkeys            List monkeys
GET /monkeys/:id        Get a monkey by id
POST /monkeys           Create a monkey
PUT /monkeys/:id        Update a moneky by id
DELETE /monkeys/:id     Delete a monkey by id
